snippet.title: Johnny Depp Received SERIOUS THREATS From Amber Heard's Father
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Received SERIOUS THREATS From Amber Heard's Father. 
Is Johnny Depp's life in danger? Well, that’s the question on everybody’s minds following the recent alleged threat to his life. In recent times, threats to injure the Pirates of the Caribbean star have come to light and these threats were issued by none other than his former father-in-law, David Heard. Things seem to have escalated beyond the courtroom for the actor and his ex-wife, Amber Heard, and her father is taking center stage in recent events. In today’s video, we’ll be revealing how Amber Heard's father seriously threatens Johnny Depp.
